snippet.title: Evertried - Kickstarter Trailer #2
snippet.description:
Kickstarter link: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/500345756/evertried/description

FREE DEMO AVAILABLE IN THE KICKSTARTER PAGE

Evertried is an isometric tactical roguelite made for PC.

Outmaneuver enemies, create traps, acquire powers and climb an eerie tower in search for the afterlife!
